/* January 2021 */
I suggested changes on Wikipedia article: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Addiko_Bank. Addiko Bank is my employer.

As the current references used for Addiko Bank dates from 2014 to 2016, I propose significant changes according to the latest sources as the current information are not up to date, e.g. the ownership, the scope of business, general information, incomplete history, irrelevant and inaccurate facts about  Hypo Alpe Adria Mostar i Banja Luka, among others. Also, infobx is updated now with the 2019 facts.
